  "Description": "\u00c2\u00a9 Copyright 2017 Blue Cross/Blue Shield of Kansas City\n\nCALLED BY : BlueKCCommonPerceptiveAPIDocStorageSeq\n\n\nPROCESSING : Job updates LetterQueueID Status in COMM table\n\nMODIFICATIONS :\n\nDeveloper                               Date                         Project                                   Change Description            Development Project          Code Reviewer                   Date Reviewed       \n------------------------------              ------------------        ----------------------             ---------------------------------------       ------------------------------\\(9)----------------------------------         -------------------------------        \nBharani Chalamalasetty      04/01/2020             Fullfillment                       Original Programming               OutboundDev3                    Jaideep Mankala              04/20/2020\n\nSaranya A                                2021-06-29            US370660         Modified Job to process NextPage and RightFax    OutboundDev3          Jaideep Mankala                 06/30/2021\n\\(9)\\(9)\\(9)\\(9)\\(9)\\(9)jobs in Parallel\n\nAnnotations:\nDSJobStartTimestamp used instead of Timestamp variable as rows need to be updated with new timestamp."
